  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\n\n### User Story\n\nAs a user, I want to see unread badge is updated when new messages are coming and app window is minimized.\n\n### Description\n\n*Type*: Bug\n\n*Summary*: when some chat is selected and new messages are coming for this chat, unread badge doesn't show new messages when app is minimized.\n\n#### Expected behavior\nUnread message is updated, because user didn't see messages\n\n#### Actual behavior\nall messages are marked as read immediately regardless of app is minimized or not.\nI would prefer to see all incoming messages as new when app is minimized, so it means that it is in the background.\n\n### Reproduction\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\n\n- Open Status\n- Start chat with user A\n- Minimize app\n- As user A, send message to 1-1 chat\n\n### Additional Information\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\n* Status version: nightly 20/11/11\n* Operating System: Mac OSx\n* Video: http://take.ms/Ywdus\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://api.monosnap.com/rpc/file/download?id=GzntLNy5x7UTel1AIpk8KfrdP3bS2d&type=preview\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div>Monosnap screenshot tool</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://monosnap.com/file/GzntLNy5x7UTel1AIpk8KfrdP3bS2d\">File \"screencast 2018-11-20 17-08-52.mp4\"</a></strong></div><div>Monosnap â€” the best tool to take & share your screenshots.</div></blockquote>",
